originalText.text: I've been going to Dr Myers for MANY YEARS and find her to be ABSOLUTELY fantastic as is her partner Dr.Sargent. She takes excellent care of each person and shows a personal interest in EVERY patient. She's stern when necessary but always with a compassionate caring Spirit. She's one of the BEST for patient care.

originalText.text:
This is one of the most family friendly practices I've been going here for roughly 5yrs and I wouldn't go any where else the entire staff knows me, my family, and all of our kids. They are always friendly and professional and never too busy to help.

Dr. Myers was caring and thorough with my exam. The personnel in the office were friendly and knowledgeable.

I had a horrible experience at a office up the street and came here. I've had many doctors in my life and now would go nowhere else!
